<div class="page-header" align="center" id="banner">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-sm-6">
<h1>mHealth Labs Project Deck</h1>
<p class="lead">The current projects underway, approved by the mHealth executive committee, updated in real-time</p>
</div>

<div class="col-sm-6">
<p>

<a href = "#completedbookm" style="color:#4caf50">completed</a>&nbsp;
